珍湯條方一樣架, 你可以拎個盒泥對下, 多料過黑金隻四物飲"},{"pid":"251c1d2c3b49141764805041341ff3a3d668ef42","tid":341661,"uid":22605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T18:53:23.000Z","msg":"龜苓膏 過一兩日就黎"},{"pid":"aa13697884e95e48e7903e7de87f84c7273785cc","tid":341661,"uid":13335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T18:00:58.000Z","msg":"平時好準31～32日就黎<br />\n上個月冇啦啦遲左勁多<br />\n50日先黎，黑黑地又多血塊<br />\n今個月又已經遲左五日<br />\n但中間有試過有啲血絲<br />\n唔知咩事睇西醫又話冇野<br />\n有冇好中醫介紹（唔好咁貴）"},{"pid":"47c56a0f98948cfecea5e29b9d87c66e55a63b2c","tid":341661,"uid":82103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T18:14:59.000Z","msg":"不如你試下唔好咁上心先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa2c3d74fce8f67f1866706c0a939cb858e5bbe8","tid":341661,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T02:40:01.000Z","msg":"我會食藥調經 好準時黎"},{"pid":"b9d3024d54187cac833c0f93b285bc2eb625dbb5","tid":341661,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:23:01.000Z","msg":"又係我<br />\n經上次遲左3星期之後<br />\n今次遲左一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n驗左4次都冇.. 應該都係冇架啦<br />\n但食極中藥都唔黎<br />\n今次直頭食活血藥都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家仲有咩方法"},{"pid":"e2c47fe2cc25e8fea4ee4b61cdcf4c21621d55ee","tid":341661,"uid":45627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T08:44:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>又係我<br />\n經上次遲左3星期之後<br />\n今次遲左一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n驗左4次都冇.. 應該都係冇架啦<br />\n但食極中藥都唔黎<br />\n今次直頭食活血藥都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家仲有咩方法</blockquote><br />\n其實絲打有冇去照過?<br />\n會唔會係有多囊卵巢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a611f56d7238032068c8252ec9349b9822c737e4","tid":341661,"uid":78770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:05:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>又係我<br />\n經上次遲左3星期之後<br />\n今次遲左一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n驗左4次都冇.. 應該都係冇架啦<br />\n但食極中藥都唔黎<br />\n今次直頭食活血藥都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家仲有咩方法</blockquote><br />\n其實絲打有冇去照過?<br />\n會唔會係有多囊卵巢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇照過呀..<br />\n平時都係 一個月加一星期咁黎..<br />\n依家不停遲到真係好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00eaa5514be7c20ff43b8acde10dc8bbd75ecd34","tid":341661,"uid":45627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T09:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>又係我<br />\n經上次遲左3星期之後<br />\n今次遲左一個月<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n驗左4次都冇.. 應該都係冇架啦<br />\n但食極中藥都唔黎<br />\n今次直頭食活血藥都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家仲有咩方法</blockquote><br />\n其實絲打有冇去照過?<br />\n會唔會係有多囊卵巢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇照過呀..<br />\n平時都係 一個月加一星期咁黎..<br />\n依家不停遲到真係好大壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果長期都係咁, 去照照比較好<br />\n我今個月都因為做嘢太忙加上食藥<br />\n遲咗成十日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係好煩<br />\n絲打你都可以留意下通常係因咩事而遲"}]}